x4freetext: mode, beam frequency 2 MHz, pulse width 2 nsec,
+-(30-60) keV for EN less then 2 MeV,
+-(50-120) keV for EN more then 3 MeV
Curium samples compositions are given in proper Subents
Standard Pu-239 samples have mass 55-150 microgram,
Pu-242 content is 1.2E-5%, Pu-244 content is 4.9E-6%
.The parasitic neutrons generated in neutron targets
measured by replacing the real targets with adequate
was less than 1% , for (d,n) reaction it was (1-4)%
Spectra of neutrons scattered by material of neutron
target were calculated by using Monte-Carlo method .
